# ZAIKA – Responsive Restaurant Website

A modern and responsive restaurant website designed to provide an engaging and seamless user experience. The project showcases a clean user interface, smooth navigation, and responsive design principles, making it accessible across desktops, tablets, and mobile devices.

##  Features

* Responsive design for all screen sizes
* Interactive navigation bar
* Modern landing page
* Food menu section
* About Us section
* Services section
* Customer testimonials
* Contact section
* Smooth scrolling and animations
* Clean and intuitive user interface

## Tech Stack

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript

##  Project Structure

```
Restaurant-Website/
│── index.html
│── css/
│── js/
│── README.md

```

